And that is why the pre-registration package is the most vital part of this entire stack.

35:44.380 --> 35:47.460
Fliction pre-registered rigorous, falsifiable experiments

35:47.460 --> 35:51.000
to prove that this math actually works in the real world.

35:51.000 --> 35:53.460
Fliction calls this the constraint horizon.

